MISSION

ForgeAI is a scalable FPGA-based AI compute architecture designed
from first principles.

The long-term objective is to create a modular AI accelerator
capable of performing high-speed matrix computation while
presenting itself to the host computer as a single compute device.

DESIGN PHILOSOPHY

• FPGA First

• Modular Design

• Parallel Compute

• Hardware Verified

• Scalable Architecture

• Professional Documentation

DESIGN STANDARDS

Clock:
    Positive Edge Triggered

Reset:
    Active High
    Synchronous

Enable:
    Active High

Default Register Width:
    8-bit unless otherwise specified

